# BugBot 项目审查规则

## 安全
- Flag any use of `eval()`, `exec()`, or `Function()` constructor
- Check for hardcoded secrets, API keys, or passwords

## 代码质量
- Backend changes (server/**, api/**) must include tests
- Deprecated APIs should be flagged

## 风格
- TODO/FIXME comments must reference an issue number (e.g., TODO(#123))
